Expert on Demand | Allow Access to the Integration in Control Hub
When you restrict user access to integrations in Control Hub, you must include the Expert on Demand integration in your allow list.
1
From the customer view in https://admin.webex.com, go to Settings, scroll to Integrations and then click Manage.
2
Find the correct integration for your release of Expert on Demand:
For Expert on Demand 1.5.1 or later, search for and select the Connected Worker integration.
For Expert on Demand 1.5.0 or earlier, search for and select the Remote Worker integration.
3
In the Overview window, choose Allow access.
4
Toggle Access for new users to On, click All users to give this permission to all your users, and then click Save.